<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Option 3</span></strong></p>
<p><strong>What it looks like:</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded" style="display:none"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;click&nbsp;to&nbsp;replay</a></div>
