<h2 id="toc9"><span>Custom Image Block Format</span></h2>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Option 1</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-20" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-20')">20</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>What it looks like:</strong></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://smlt.wikidot.com/local--files/mrpines:choo-choo/train3.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="enlarge" alt="train3.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Hover your mouse over the image to make it enlarge.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>What to copy:</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:image-zoom&#32;name={$name}|caption={$caption}|width=300px|align=right]]</span></p>
</div>
<p>Change <strong>{$name}</strong> to the filename or link to the image. Change <strong>{$caption}</strong> to the text you want under the image. The width and alignment are set to the standard for SCP articles, but those can be changed as well.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Option 2</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-21" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-21')">21</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>What it looks like:</strong></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://smlt.wikidot.com/local--files/mrpines:choo-choo/train3.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="unblur" alt="train3.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Hover your mouse over the image to view it.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>What to copy:</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:image-blur&#32;name={$name}|caption={$caption}|width=300px|align=right]]</span></p>
</div>
<p>Change <strong>{$name}</strong> to the filename or link to the image. Change <strong>{$caption}</strong> to the text you want under the image. The width and alignment are set to the standard for SCP articles, but those can be changed as well.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Option 3</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-22" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-22')">22</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>What it looks like:</strong></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://smlt.wikidot.com/local--files/mrpines:choo-choo/train3.jpg" title="Click and hold to enlarge." style="width:300px;" class="fillpg" alt="train3.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Click and hold to enlarge the image.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>What to copy:</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:component:image-zoom-2&#32;name={$name}|caption={$caption}|width=300px|align=right]]</span></p>
</div>
<p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> This will not work properly unless your image has .png or .jpg as a file extension.</p>
<p>Change <strong>{$name}</strong> to the filename or link to the image. Change <strong>{$caption}</strong> to the text you want under the image. The width and alignment are set to the standard for SCP articles, but those can be changed as well.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
