<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-17"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-17')">17</a>. As seen in <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4003">SCP-4003</a></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-18"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-18')">18</a>. <strong>Source:</strong> <a href="http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wikidot.com/inc:fakeprot">http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wikidot.com/inc:fakeprot</a><br />
<strong>Original Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nanimono-demonai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1703549); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1703549&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="Nanimono Demonai" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1703549)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nanimono-demonai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1703549); return false;">Nanimono Demonai</a></span></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-19"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-19')">19</a>. As seen in <a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/scp-1370-jp">SCP-1370-JP</a>.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-20"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-20')">20</a>. As seen in <a href="/scp-4224">SCP-4224</a>, <a href="/scp-4577">SCP-4577</a>, and <a href="/scp-3662">SCP-3662</a></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-21"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-21')">21</a>. As seen in <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/error-field-cannot-be-lloyd">ERROR: Field Cannot Be Lloyd</a></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-22"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-22')">22</a>. As seen in <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/hawks-n-artworks">Hawks n Artworks</a></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-23"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-23')">23</a>. Translated into SCP-CN by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sekai-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4476849); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4476849&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="Sekai_s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4476849)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sekai-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4476849); return false;">Sekai_s</a></span></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-24"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-24')">24</a>. Translated into SCP-KO by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiken-drum" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2061751); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2061751&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="Aiken Drum" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2061751)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiken-drum" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2061751); return false;">Aiken Drum</a></span></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-25"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-25')">25</a>. Translated into SCP-JP by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/7happy7" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3427263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3427263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="7happy7" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3427263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/7happy7" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3427263); return false;">7happy7</a></span></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-26"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-26')">26</a>. Transleted into SCP-IT by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jyj-52" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5378646); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5378646&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="jyj_52" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5378646)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jyj-52" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5378646); return false;">jyj_52</a></span></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-27"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-27')">27</a>. Credit for both of these goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nanimono-demonai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1703549); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1703549&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="Nanimono Demonai" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1703549)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nanimono-demonai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1703549); return false;">Nanimono Demonai</a></span>.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-28"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-28')">28</a>. Credit goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-take" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872372); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2872372&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="C-take" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2872372)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-take" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872372); return false;">C-take</a></span> from the JP branch.<br />
<strong>Source:</strong> <a href="http://shitake-crude-production.wikidot.com/javascript:timeviewer">http://shitake-crude-production.wikidot.com/javascript:timeviewer</a></div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-29"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-29')">29</a>. <strong>Source:</strong> <a href="http://smlt.wikidot.com/boyu12:inc-loop">http://smlt.wikidot.com/boyu12:inc-loop</a><br />
<strong>Original Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boyu12" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3316163); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3316163&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609170689" alt="Boyu12" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3316163)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boyu12" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3316163); return false;">Boyu12</a></span></div>
